{
  "stem": "18960.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one day, after the appell-- after the so-called appell, they call it, the-- at evening-- they always called out number-- always called numbers with people to pick up packages or for other reasons.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They called for the-- for instance, every day for another Jehovah's Witness, see if wants to resign from his faith, they will let him go.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They never called me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One day, they're calling me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I almost fainted, and thought, ah, they discovered me already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They-- they got a letter from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They're going to shoot and going to execute me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I'm going there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They said, no, you have a package there-- pick up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I am going there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There's a big package.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I could hardly carry it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I bring it to my-- to my block-- from her parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But and then soon enough, shortly after, I got a letter with regards asking me different questions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I brought this-- this package had a double purpose for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Number one, it legitimized me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was also get-- also family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Of course, I had to make up a story that why I don't get packages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My-- my parent-- my parents were-- were deported to Siberia and they were shot and I was left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was more-- more believable, that actually getting packages and getting letters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was-- I started to live it up, because first of all, in that package, there was real good stuff.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had even a stuffed-- a stuffed duck with apples inside, fat-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do you call this fat from pigs?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lard.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, lard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lard, melted lard, bread cakes-- I started sharing this food with-- with a group of my friends, Poles, and they became very friendly with me.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
